      "span_text": "The studies by Winham et al. [CITATION_2] , conducted on the population of more than 400 imprisoned women on parole, indicate that the insecure attachment (evaluated with the AAS -Adult Attachment Scale) is the mediation between child victimization and the symptoms of psychological distress."
